\c 5
\s Dhavhidhi anokumbira kuti afambiswe zvakanaka pakati pavavengi vake
\d Kumutungamiriri wenziyo; nenyere. Pisarema raDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Inzwai mashoko angu Jehovha,Rangarirai kufunga komoyo wangu.
\v 2 teererai inzwi rokuchema kwangu, imwi Mambo wangu naMwari wangu; nekuti ndinonyengetera kwamuri.
\v 3 Jehovha, muchanzwa inzwi rangu mangwanani;Mangwanani ndichakurongedzerai munyengetero wangu,ndichirindira.
\v 4 Nekuti hamuzi Mwari anofarira zvakaipa, munhu, akashata, haangagari nemi.
\v 5 Munhu anozvikudza haangamiriri pamberi penyu; Munovenga vose vanoita zvakaipa.
\v 6 Muchaparadza anoreva nhema; Jehovha anosema munhu anoteura ropa neanonyengera.
\v 7 Asi kana ndirini, ndichapinda mumba menyu nekuwanda kwevunyoro bwenyu, Ndichanamata ndakaringira kutemberi yenyu tsvene ndichikutyai.
\v 8 Ndifambisei, Jehovha, mukururama kwenyu nekuda kwavavengi vangu; Gadzirai nzira yenyu pamberi pangu.
\v 9 Nekuti hapana kutendeka pamiromo yavo; Mukati mavo makashata-shata; huro dzavo bwiro bwakashama; Vanobata kumeso norurimi rwavo.
\v 10 Muvapei, mhosva, Jehovha ngavawe namano avo;Nokuti vakakumukirai.
\v 11 Asi vose vanovimba nemwi ngavafare, Ngavadanidzire nomufaro nguva dzose,nokuti imwi munovadzitira; Vose vanoda zita renyu ngavafare nemi.
\v 12 Nekuti mucharopafadza akarurama; imwi Jehovha, muchamukomberedza nenyasha senhovo.
